title: How Adulting Works
description:
Your Adulting Instruction Manual

Life does not come with an instruction manual. It should.

You are expected to find a job, handle finances, pay taxes, vote, buy a car, buy property, raise children, and organise committees - all with no instruction manual.

This podcast tackles adulting skills in a story-based, easy to consume, format. We talk to experts, doers, and those who are winning in adulting, and share their knowledge with you.

This is your adulting instruction manual.
